Juventus progressed to the Coppa Italia final after beating Fiorentina 2-1 in the first leg of the semi-final . 
  Alessandro Matri scored the opening goal of the game before Roberto Pereyra doubled the lead . 
  Alvaro Morata was sent off for a foul on Alessandro Diamanti . 
  Leonardo Bonucci scored the third for Juventus in the second half . 
  Juventus will face Napoli or Lazio in the final . 
 